<h3 id="situations-that-our-application-can-help-you-with">Situations that our application can help you with</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Make food</strong> in our kitchen
    <ul>
      <li>With the ingredients we have
        <ul>
          <li>Order ingredients online</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Within the time we have</li>
      <li>With the utensils we have</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Order food</strong> on-line
    <ul>
      <li>Based on rating</li>
      <li>From our favorite restaurant</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Go out</strong> and eat
    <ul>
      <li>Best restaurants nearby</li>
      <li>Restaurant details, reviews and ratings</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

